title: Fall in love with the iconic Austin City Skyline!
posting_body: ['Text ID # 5226A to my cell for more info!', "Come home to the most luxurious apartments in Downtown Austin, and relish in high-end living in the heart of Austin's most trendy neighborhood.", 'Our studio, one, and two bedroom apartment homes offer spacious layouts and include top-of-the-line amenities.', "We all love the iconic Austin city skyline, but it's so much better from your couch or bed (just trust us on that one), especially when you live on the top floor!", 'Inside your apartment home, you will find floor-to-ceiling windows with eco-friendly living features including a Nest programmable thermostat along with USB outlets and ENERGYSTAR stainless appliances, making your home energy efficient and tech-friendly.', 'You will also live a life of luxury in your contemporary chef-inspired kitchen with modern flat cabinets featuring a frosted glass inlay, coordinating white quartz and subway tile backsplash, plus unique appliances such as a bottom freezer refrigerator and glass stove top.', 'Overlooking breathtaking views of the Downtown Austin skyline, an eighth floor deck full of rooftop amenities.', 'Bask in our resort-style, infinity edge pool, with stunning ledges and grilling stations open up to breathtaking panoramas of the Austin city skyline.', 'You can also treat your friends to your luxurious lifestyle by renting out our rooftop lounge equipped with a professional demonstration kitchen and large entertaining area for your next social gathering.', 'Need a workspace outside of your office?', 'Our 24/7 tech lounge is equipped with speedy WIFI and full access printer.', 'You can also stop paying for your pricey gym membership and enjoy our modern 24-hour fitness studio with cardio equipment, weight machines, and free weights as well as a yoga studio.', "Plus, feel good about your apartment's impact on the environment because our building is Green Label Gold LEED Certified"]
